    "description": "FP InovoLabs GmbH is a wholly-owned subsidiary of Francotyp-Postalia Holding AG (FP), one of the leading global suppliers of mail center solutions. A major component of FP’s business is the production and support of postal franking machines (postage meters). These postal franking machines incorporate a postal security device (PSD) that performs all postage meter cryptographic and postal security functions and which protects both Critical Security Parameters (CSPs) and Postal Relevant Data Items (PRDIs) from unauthorized access. The Postal NRevenector GB 2019 is FP’s latest generation of PSD.",
